n]}','{}','{\n  \"Will our hard-won progress in health development be set back, as happened in some parts of the world following the emergence and spread of HIV/AIDS?\\n\\n\": \"会不会像世界上一些地区在艾滋病毒/艾滋病出现并扩散后所发生的那样，卫生发展领域来之不易的进展出现倒退？\\n\",\n  \"But, it warns this progress could be set back if measures are not taken to reverse the rise in obesity among young people.\\n\\n\": \"但是，该机构提醒到，如果不采取措施逆转年轻人中不断增加的肥胖情况，这种进展可能会发生倒退。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \" 推迟；使…受挫折；把…往回拨\": \"wait,phase back,\"\n}','/voice/set backmei.mp3','/voice/set backying.mp3','0','0'),('set down','','','{[\n  \"{放下；记下；看做；确定:放下；记下；看做；确定}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"Then he stopped and set down the tool.\\n\\n\": \"突然，他停了下来，放下工具。\\n\",\n  \"Let me set down here part of what I wrote in a letter, at a more advanced age, about the Morning Songs.\\n\\n\": \"让我在这里记下我在上了年纪时，所写的关于《晨歌集》的信件中的一部分。\\n\",\n  \"One of the choppers set down on the beach below them, the other on the bluff above.\\n\\n\": \"有一架直升机在他们下面的海滩上降落，其余的直接降落在断崖上。\\n\"\n}','{}','/voice/set downmei.mp3','/voice/set downying.mp3','0','0'),('set fire to','','','{[\n  \"{点燃，使燃烧:点燃，使燃烧}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"Officials say some angry about the attack fired shots into the air and set fire to nearby vehicles.\\n\\n\": \"有关官员说，自杀袭击激怒了一些人，他们朝天开枪，并点燃附近的车辆。\\n\",\n  \"A boy set fire to a firework, and it burned on the sticks.\\n\\n\": \"一个男孩点燃了一个爆竹，爆竹在木柴上燃烧起来。\\n\",\n  \"Police banned the sale of tires in Bangkok without police permits so demonstrators couldn\'t set fire to them around the city.\\n\\n\": \"为让示威者不能在城市各处点燃轮胎，警方禁止在没有警方许可的情况下在曼谷销售轮胎。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \" 点燃，使燃烧\": \"emblaze,ignite,\"\n}','/voice/set fire tomei.mp3','/voice/set fire toying.mp3','0','0'),('set foot on','','','{[\n  \"{踏上:踏上}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"We fear they\'ll tell us our product or service stinks, that we\'re horrible people and we should never have set foot on earth.\\n\\n\": \"我们害怕他们告诉我们的产品和服务很差，我们是很讨厌的人，我们不应该在地球踏上一步。\\n\",\n  \"Have you ever wished you could take a pill that mimics all the positive benefits of exercise without ever having to set foot on the Stairmaster?\\n\\n\": \"你是否曾经盼望过，只要吞下一粒药，你甚至不用踏上台阶机，就能取得酷似锻炼带来的所有积极效果？\\n\",\n  \"They were among the first words World Bank President Paul Wolfowitz spoke as he set foot on the ground in Aceh, the first leg of his trip to Indonesia and Timor Leste.\\n\\n\": \"世界银行行长保罗.沃尔福威茨在踏上亚齐的土地之后所说的第一句话中，就包含了这两个字。 这里是他印度尼西亚和东帝汶行程的第一站。\\n\"\n}','{}','/voice/set foot onmei.mp3','/voice/set foot onying.mp3','0','0'),('set forth','','','{[\n  \"{陈述，提出；出发；陈列；宣布:陈述，提出；出发；陈列；宣布}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"This evening I will set forth policies to advance that ideal at home and around the world.\\n\\n\": \"今天晚上，我将提出为在国内和全世界推进这一理念所必需的政策。\\n\",\n  \"What I may decide about, what comes to the Faith Council is advancing some of the priority areas that the President has set forth one of which is interfaith cooperation.\\n\\n\": \"我能够决定的，信仰委员会所负责的,是推进一些重点领域,一些总统提出来的重点领域的发展,其中一点就是跨信仰合作。\\n\",\n  \"He set forth from the Canaries in a rubber dinghy, with all food on board locked away.\\n\\n\": \"他乘坐一艘橡皮艇从西拔牙的加纳丽群岛出发，把船上携带的食品锁了起来。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \" 陈述，提出；出发；陈列；宣布\": \"introduce,present,speak,prefer,leave,\"\n}','/voice/set forthmei.mp3','/voice/set forthying.mp3','0','0');
INSERT INTO `mfg_t_wordtest` VALUES ('set free','','','{[\n  \"{v: 释放；使获得自由}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"Undoubtedly, Galileo was a great thinker who risked much in the pursuit of truth, helping to set free the quest for knowledge from the chains of religious dogmatism.\\n\\n\": \"毋庸置疑的是伽利略是一位伟大的思想家，在追求真理的道路上他勇于挑战，为将知识从宗教教条主义中解放出来做出了巨大贡献。\\n\",\n  \"He wore a badly-fitting ready-made suit and the cheap shoes that the state gives to prisoners, when they are set free.\\n\\n\": \"他穿着一套很不合身的现成衣服和一双廉价的鞋子。 这些是在释放犯人时发给他们的。\\n\",\n  \"Breathing it, Robert felt as if he was set free from a cage.\\n\\n\": \"呼吸着空气，罗伯特感觉自己像是被人从牢笼释放出来一般。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \"v\": \"let loose,let go of,\"\n}','/voice/set freemei.mp3','/voice/set freeying.mp3','0','0'),('set in','','','{[\n  \"{vi: 开始；到来；流行}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"Perhaps that is as it should be for a film set in Iraq.\\n\\n\": \"也许这是因为它本来就是一部设定在伊拉克的电影。\\n\",\n  \"The spring-sowing time has set in.\\n\\n\": \"春播季节到来了。\\n\",\n  \"The rainy season has set in.\\n\\n\": \"雨季已经开始了。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \"vi\": \"proceed,obtain,\"\n}','/voice/set inmei.mp3','/voice/set inying.mp3','0','0'),('set in motion','','','{[\n  \"{开始，调动；把…发动起来:开始，调动；把…发动起来}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"What else does that stone Commander signify, that cold statue set in motion to punish the blood and courage that dared to think?\\n\\n\": \"那位高级骑士的石像还代表了什么呢？ 那个冰冷的雕像为了惩罚敢于思考的热血和勇气而开始运动。\\n\",\n  \"That should set in motion a long-planned chain of events, starting with the formation of an interim government that will run the country for about a year while overseeing preparations for elections.\\n\\n\": \"将设定一项包括多项长期计划的议案，包括开始组建临时政府来保持国家运转大约一年，同时监督选举的准备工作。\\n\",\n  \"During the meeting “we\'ll discuss how we stop the hyper-partisanship plaguing Washington and how we can set in motion an upward spiral of confidence in our economy and our politics.\\n\\n\": \"在这次集会“我们将讨论如何永超党派的关系结束华盛顿的困境和如何我们能够把人们对于我们经济和政治的信心调动起来。”\\n\"\n}','{\n  \" 开始，调动；把…发动起来\": \"institute,proceed,remove,initiate,\"\n}','/voice/set in motionmei.mp3','/voice/set in motionying.mp3','0','0'),('set off','','[,set \'ɔf]','{[\n  \"{v: 出发；引起；动身；使爆炸；抵销；分开}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"The next morning, we set off.\\n\\n\": \"次日上午我们出发了。\\n\",\n  \"Soon after that, Gawain set off to look for the Green Knight to receive his cut.\\n\\n\": \"不久以后，高文爵士便出发寻找绿衣骑士，去接受那许下的一斧。\\n\",\n  \"Fired up by this encounter, we set off for Croatia and the Adriatic.\\n\\n\": \"在这次会见的鼓舞下，我们出发前往克罗地亚和亚得里亚海。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \"v\": \"set out,set loose,\"\n}','/voice/set offmei.mp3','/voice/set offying.mp3','0','0'),('set out','','','{[\n  \"{出发；开始；陈述；陈列:出发；开始；陈述；陈列}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"Then they set out.\\n\\n\": \"然后他们出发。\\n\",\n  \"The troops are about to set out.\\n\\n\": \"部队就要出发了。\\n\",\n  \"Nobby and I set out for Croydon.\\n\\n\": \"诺比和我向克罗伊登方向出发。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \" 出发；开始；陈述；陈列\": \"institute,proceed,speak,leave,start off,\"\n}','/voice/set outmei.mp3','/voice/set outying.mp3','0','0'),('set out to','','','{[\n  \"{打算，着手:打算，着手}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"Sam set out to improve efficiency at the shirt factory but, as we find out later in this unit, his plans turned out not quite as he had expected.\\n\\n\": \"萨姆着手提高衬衫厂的效率了，但正如我们将在本课后半部分发现的，他的计划实施结果跟他原先预料的并不完全一样。\\n\",\n  \"While there are evil people who simply set out to commit frauds, few frauds of the nature we are seeing in China start out that way.\\n\\n\": \"虽然的确有些大奸大恶之徒一开始就打算好了要舞弊，但是，我们在中国看到的这些舞弊中，很少是这个样子的。\\n\"\n}','{\n  \" 打算，着手\": \"propose,think,\"\n}','/voice/set out tomei.mp3','/voice/set out toying.mp3','0','0'),('set sail','','','{[\n  \"{启航；张帆:启航；张帆}\"\n]}','{}','{\n  \"It probably set sail from Guangzhou, the largest of the ports linked by the Maritime Silk Route.\\n\\n\": \"而且很有可能事在广州启航，当时的广州是海上丝绸之路的港口中最大的港口。\\n\",\n  \"Believing that Asia could be reached by traveling westward, Columbus\'s three-ship expedition set sail from Palos, Spain, in 1492.\\n\\n\": \"1492年，坚信向西航行能抵达亚洲的哥伦布，带领他的三艘远征船从西班牙的帕洛斯起航了。\\n\",\n  \"In 1966, Hubbard—who by then had met and married anot